{"tid":2422615,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"涉黃大仙非法集結 23歲男子罪成判入戒毒所","createTime":"2021-02-25T10:07:37.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T10:07:37.000Z","uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"4ebc3928ef43de7b56870803346a3a0418e11d50","tid":2422615,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T10:07:37.000Z","msg":"2019年8月24日，有示威者在黃大仙龍翔道堵路，一名23歲男子被捕。 被告早前否認控罪，經審訊後被裁定「參與非法集結」罪成，今日（2月24日）在觀塘裁判法院被判入戒毒所。 裁判官判刑時指，非法集結是嚴重罪行，即時監禁是無可避免，考慮到被告有濫藥問題，判被告入戒毒所，並留下刑事定罪紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n- 熱血時報網站連結 <a href=\"https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-24-2021/70700\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F02-24-2021%2F70700&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFcvW%2Fvk9QtnWk1JKGKfj%2Fbg%3D&h=e8a13564\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.passiontimes.hk/article/02-24-2021/70700</a><br />\n- Copyright &copy; 2021"}]}